8
00:00:33,840 --> 00:00:33,909
Scott: Yep.

9
00:00:34,341 --> 00:00:36,840
Scott: I mean, I've been reading Dilbert for a long time.

10
00:00:36,860 --> 00:00:38,640
Scott: And perhaps as long as Dilbert has existed.

11
00:00:39,221 --> 00:00:41,199
Scott: And I always knew all of it was true.

12
00:00:42,224 --> 00:00:43,058
Scott: And it, yeah.

13
00:00:43,640 --> 00:00:51,224
