110
00:06:13,963 --> 00:06:14,918
Rym: Yeah, voice over IP.

111
00:06:15,624 --> 00:06:15,720
Rym: VoIP.

112
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:17,420
Scott: It's just an internet phone, basically.

113
00:06:19,141 --> 00:06:22,199
